<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
       <img src="/assets/gift.png" alt="Sample Image" height="180px" width="180px">
       <div class="list group">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-gift"></span>
          <span class="badge">10</span>
          Gift Requests
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></span>
          <span class="badge">10</span>
          Comments
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></span>
          <span class="badge">10</span>
          Followers
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-asterisk"></span>
          <span class="badge">10</span>
          Following
        </li>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8 left-block">
    <div class="info-block">
      <div class="info-text">
        <h3> <%= @user.username %></h3>
        
         
         <p>Proin vitae volutpat tellus. Fusce erat libero, ultrices in egestas id, tincidunt quis ante. Nam volutpat purus sed justo hendrerit, ac pellentesque odio volutpat. Integer vitae purus tortor. Aenean ultricies porta rhoncus. Nullam eleifend, tortor quis porta consectetur, enim nunc rutrum erat, ut convallis augue libero ac orci.

          Aenean ultricies porta rhoncus eleifend tortor quis.</p>
          
        </div>
        <div class="list">
          <ul class="list-group inverse-theme">
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <h4>Summary</h4>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <span class="badge"><%=current_user.points%></span>
              Points:
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <span class="badge"><%=current_user.rank%></span>
              Rank:
            </li>
          </ul>
          <% if current_user == @user && @user.authentications.nil? %>
          <p> When your account is connected with facebook, you can login to your same account using with 1 click. You can also easily share your gift requests and get better answers from your friends </p>
          <a id="facebook_login_button" href=<%= ENV['FACEBOOK_LOGIN_URL'] %> class="popup" data-height="400" data-width="600"><%= image_tag "fb-connect.png", :style => "width: ;height:38px; padding-top:1px;" %></a>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-info btn-large"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus"></span>
      </i> Follow</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Nav tabs -->
  <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
    <li class="active"><a href="#recentactivity" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Recent Activity</a></li>
    <li><a href="#giftrequests" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Gift Requests</a></li>
    <li><a href="#comments" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Comments</a></li>
    <li><a href="#badges" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Badges</a></li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Tab panes -->
  <div class="tab-content">
    <div class="tab-pane fade in active" id="recentactivity">
      <h2>Recent Activity: </h2>

      <% @activity.each do |activity| %>

      <p> <%= activity["message"] %> </p>

      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="giftrequests">...</div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="comments">...</div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="badges">...</div>
  </div>

</div>